<title>Download the Windows 10 Creators Update Now</title>
<link>http://feeds.tweaks.com/~r/WinTweaks/~3/9mJMBP5AOyU/</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://feeds.tweaks.com/~r/WinTweaks/~3/9mJMBP5AOyU/</guid>
<description>&lt;p&gt;Microsoft released the Windows 10 Creators Update (AKA version 1703, build 15063) to the public on April 5th, 2017. The fully automated update via Windows Update is not yet available (you must wait until April 10th), but you can trigger the update manually now.  In addition, you can create bootable USB media or a DVD ISO file for a fresh install. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manual Update&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you already have Windows 10 and want to manually trigger the update, you can &lt;a href=&quot;http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=799445&quot;&gt;download and run the Windows 10 Upgrade utility&lt;/a&gt;.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then, Just click the &lt;strong&gt;Update Now&lt;/strong&gt; button. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://cdn.tweaks.com/img/article/downlaodwin10cu.png&quot; alt=&quot;Manually update to Windows 10 Creators Update&quot; width=&quot;700&quot; height=&quot;489&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Media Creator&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to perform a clean install of the Windows 10 Creators Update, you can &lt;a href=&quot;http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=691209&quot;&gt;download the media creation tool&lt;/a&gt;.  After downloading, run MediaCreationTool.exe. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then, click through the license agreement, select &lt;strong&gt;Create installation media (USB flash drive, DVD, or ISO file for another PC&lt;/strong&gt; and click &lt;strong&gt;Next&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://cdn.tweaks.com/img/article/downloadwin10cu1.png&quot; alt=&quot;Downloading Windows 10 Creators Update ISO&quot; width=&quot;702&quot; height=&quot;555&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Confirm the recommended language, edition and architecture and click &lt;strong&gt;Next&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://cdn.tweaks.com/img/article/downloadwin10cu2.png&quot; alt=&quot;Downloading Windows 10 Creators Update ISO&quot; width=&quot;702&quot; height=&quot;555&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Finally, select either the USB flash drive option or ISO file and click &lt;strong&gt;Next&lt;/strong&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://cdn.tweaks.com/img/article/downloadwin10cu3.png&quot; alt=&quot;Downloading Windows 10 Creators Update ISO&quot; width=&quot;702&quot; height=&quot;555&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Windows 10 Creators Update will begin to download.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://cdn.tweaks.com/img/article/downloadwin10cu4.png&quot; alt=&quot;Downloading Windows 10 Creators Update ISO&quot; width=&quot;702&quot; height=&quot;555&quot;/&gt;0&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Finish&lt;/strong&gt; when the download is complete to wrap up. &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
<pubDate>Thu, 06 Apr 2017 03:15:56 +0000</pubDate>
<og:image>//tweaks.com/img/fb_logo.png</og:image>
<dc:language>en</dc:language>
<dc:format>text/html</dc:format>
<dc:identifier>http://tweaks.com/windows/67228/download-the-windows-10-creators-update-now/</dc:identifier>
</item>
